snippet.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles (Atari ST) - 01 - Bebop
snippet.description:
Oh look, another port of this game.

Another meh port, looks like it was very hastily coded.

Taken from the same pool the Commodore 64, Amiga and DOS ports were created from.
